         <div type="translation">
            <ab>"[. . . ] rose flowers, 4 drachmas together with the finest honey, [. . . ] burnt copper 8(?) drachmas and red sumach ? drachmas. Cilician saffron 2 drachmas. Now, having cut, pounded and mixed the remaining ingredients, [following line too fragmentary for translation]. For all affections in the mouth. To be applied dry."</ab>
